.TH "al_set_shader_matrix" "3" "" "Allegro reference manual" ""
.SH NAME
.PP
al_set_shader_matrix \- Allegro 5 API
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
#include\ <allegro5/allegro.h>

bool\ al_set_shader_matrix(const\ char\ *name,
\ \ \ ALLEGRO_TRANSFORM\ *matrix)
\f[]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Sets a matrix uniform of the current target bitmap\[aq]s shader.
.PP
Returns true on success.
Otherwise returns false, e.g.
if the uniform by that name does not exist in the shader.
.SH SINCE
.PP
5.1.0
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
al_use_shader(3)
